725920f-a.title: Queens: 158th Street - Liberty Avenue
725920f-a.text:
158th Street, east side, between Liberty Avenue and
Beaver Road, looking eastward and show ng the remuins of
St. Monicas Convent, adjoining Prospect Cemetery, and the
convent grounds. On the left is St. Monicas Roman Catholic
Church.
P. L. Sperr
